data.description: Welcome Home!! Large, low maintenance villa in the desirable Geneva Village at Fountain Place within the  O'Fallon School district! Upon entrance, find wood flooring which flows to the open, split bedroom floor plan.This beautiful 3 bedroom, 3-bathroom villa has a lot of space to offer! The vaulted great room and the eat-in kitchen walks out to the deck overlooking the backyard. You'll love the spacious kitchen with beautiful, abundant cabinetry and breakfast bar. Main floor private owner's suite with coffered ceiling, walk-in closet, garden tub, walk-in shower and dual vanity. Main floor complete with laundry room, separate dining room, full hall bathroom, and 2nd bedroom. The partially finished walk-out basement has all the space you need! Large family room, 3rd bedroom, full bathroom, and PLENTY of storage. This one-owner villa has the largest floor plan in the neighborhood. Close to highway access, shopping, and restaurants!. Seller offering $5,000 flooring allowance.
